CR Customer Segment Analysis Instance Record	CR Customer Segment Analysis Instance Record	Customer Segment Analysis Instance Record	##			Maintain a portfolio of analytical views of the customer base to support customer segment profitability and performance analysis	IO	IO	IO	O	IO					
			Customer Segment Type			The descriptive name of the bank defined customer segment 	IO	IO	IO	O						
			Customer Segment Type Definition			Detailed properties and characteristics that define the customer segment	IO	IO	IO	O						
			Customer Segment Performance Goals			Definition of the performance goals for defined customer segments as defined by senior management functions (target/anticipated and actual as assessed).	IO	IO	IO	O						
			Customer Segment Analysis Schedule			The schedule for performing customer segment analysis for the enterprise or division	IO	IO	IO	O	IO					
			Customer Segment Analysis Report	##		A consolidated report containing the results of performance analyses applied to the Customer Segment	IO	IO	IO	O	IO					
				Customer Segment Analysis Type 		Defines a type of performance analysis performed (e.g. scheduled review, specialized analysis, sensitivity assessment/projection)	IO	IO	IO	O	IO					
				Customer Segment Analysis Result		The consolidated report of the performance evaluation and comparisons from the analysis	O	IO	O	O	IO					
				Customer Segment Analysis Reporting Date 		The date/time the performance report was completed	IO	IO	IO	O	IO					
				Document Directory Entry Instance Reference		Reference to associated performance analysis reporting documents	O	IO	O	O	IO					
BQ Performance Analysis Instance Record	BQ Performance Analysis Instance Record	Performance Analysis Instance Record	##			The record of the specific performance analysis task - note the overall customer portfolio analysis combines multiple performance analysis perspectives					IO	IO		IO	IO	O
			Customer Segment Performance Analysis Type 			Defines the type of analysis/algorithm used to evaluate and compare the customer segment performance to prevailing market measures					IO	IO		IO	IO	O
			Customer Segment Performance Analysis Task 	##		Record of a task to perform a selected type of performance analysis on a customer segment					IO	IO		IO	IO	O
				Customer Segment Performance Request Specification		The specific details of the performance analysis (can be a default/standard analysis or a specialist/ad-hoc request)					IO	IO		IO	IO	O
				Customer Segment Performance Model Reference		Reference to the performance analysis model used					IO	IO		IO	IO	O
				Customer Segment Performance Product/Service Activity Report 		The data file, report of customer related transaction details used in the analysis					IO	IO		IO	IO	O
				Customer Segment Performance Financial Market Research Report 		The content of selected financial market research report or market transaction database in any suitable form used for comparisons when appropriate					IO	IO		IO	IO	O
				Customer Segment Performance Work Products		Work documentation, forms and schedules produced and referenced during the analysis					IO	IO		IO	IO	O
				Customer Segment Performance Request Result		The output from executing the selected performance analysis 					O	IO		IO	IO	O